on. The cancellation occurs\nbecause of the acoustic sum rule.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 May 2016 15:54:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Nov 2016 01:18:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 26 Jan 2017 16:49:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-27"}
